# =============================================================
# Honor of Kings (Global) Ruleset for Loon (Comprehensive)
#
# Description: An exhaustive ruleset for Honor of Kings (HOK)
# global version, including core game servers, Level Infinite
# publisher services, Tencent global infrastructure (GCloud, INTL),
# and anti-cheat/support dependencies.
#
# Author: Gemini
# Last Updated: 2026-04-23
# =============================================================

# Part 1: Core Game Domains
# 核心游戏域名 (王者荣耀国际版专属)
# Covers main website, game announcements, and specific event pages.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, honorofkings.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, hokglobal.com

# Part 2: Publisher Services (Level Infinite)
# 发行商服务 (Level Infinite 品牌)
# Used for publisher-level accounts, cross-game events, and web stores.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, levelinfinite.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, levelinfinitepass.com

# Part 3: Tencent Global Infrastructure
# 腾讯海外游戏底层架构与公共组件 (Proxima Beta / INTL / GCloud)
# Crucial for game login, updates, CDN downloads, and matchmaking.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, proximabeta.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, intlgame.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, igamecj.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, tencentgames.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, gcloudcs.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, tencent-cloud.com

# Part 4: Anti-Cheat & Security
# 反作弊与安全验证组件 (Anti-Cheat Expert)
# Required for game launch and background security checks.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, anticheatexpert.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, ace.tencent.com

# Part 5: Customer Support & Telemetry
# 客服系统与运行遥测
# Used for in-game help centers and crash reporting.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, helpshift.com

# Part 6: Keyword Fallbacks
# 关键词回落 (兜底规则)
# Catches unlisted CDN nodes, dynamic subdomains, or new API routes.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, honorofkings
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, hokglobal
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, levelinfinite
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, proximabeta
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, intlgame
